{"tid":1384743,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不合作運動係要比你地班自私既香港人知道","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:54:14.000Z","uid":36994,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e103cb3dbc1a24ea13efe947e086b27660a67739","tid":1384743,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"政府無正視過我地既訴求<br />\n200萬上街、每個星期既遊行<br />\n我地為你地做咁多野<br />\n你唔好一句同我講「阻你番工，好反感」<br />\n屌你老母，警黑不差別打人你唔反感？<br />\n點解反感，因為你自撚私，依家切身地阻礙到你啊麻？<br />\n其他人比人打你一定會覺得關人撚事，四隻大字<br />\n我地做左好撚多野啦，有無人理過我地啊？<br />\n阻你一陣姐，洗死咩？<br />\n係咪真係想無曬自由你地先安落？"},{"pid":"5c7841f8f89e1a017f163ee706b7131c4f978efe","tid":1384743,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"香港人係咪從1842年就咁自私？<br />\n你搞運動還搞運動 咪阻到我<br />\n你地打還打 咪打到我？"},{"pid":"fb6ace792fd8a17c2d0aae3885602b868a5ec6dd","tid":1384743,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:53:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"6e5a4b25eca54d5b9f8c7671e81c48d58762b606","tid":1384743,"uid":250118,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"你地咪繼續圍爐自high囉 <br />\n<br />\n但其他人根本唔覺得呢兩件事有關係"},{"pid":"e75eec69f0dc0b184b2dfedfeb295f2173a5d6e2","tid":1384743,"uid":36994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e5a4b25eca54d5b9f8c7671e81c48d58762b606","tid":1384743,"uid":250118,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"你地咪繼續圍爐自high囉 <br />\n<br />\n但其他人根本唔覺得呢兩件事有關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:55:12.000Z","msg":"依家咪話你知 有關囉"},{"pid":"ad8b89e1598019e18888bbf46f120d0a129baf64","tid":138